                <mxCell id="nal_timing_box" value="&lt;b&gt;Timing Model (StepTimings)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;docker_run_s: docker run → running (0.1–1 s)&lt;br&gt;network_attach_s: veth → OVS → IP (+ rs.add for storage) (1–10 s)&lt;br&gt;total_s: wall-clock, first step to last (1.5–15 s)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Logged at INFO by _log_timings() on every operation" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#d6b656;fillColor=#fff2cc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;spacingLeft=10;rounded=1;fontSize=11;" parent="1" vertex="1">
